videos.headline: No. 1 South Carolina routs Arkansas to remain unbeaten
videos.description: The Gamecocks use a 14-0 run at the start of the second quarter to take control as they improve to 28-0 overall and 15-0 in the SEC with a 98-61 win over the Hogs.

videos.headline: Watkins credits Gamecocks' success to strong teamwork
videos.description: After dropping 21 points and 11 rebounds, Ashlyn Watkins highlights No. 1 South Carolina's discipline, cohesive teamwork and commitment in its win over Arkansas.
